@database "lola"
@author Alfonso Ranieri

@Node "Main" "lola"

    @{u}@{b}lola@{ub}@{uu}
    Written by Alfonso Ranieri


    @{" Author " LINK "Author"} @{" WRID " LINK "WRID"} @{" Changes " LINK "Changes"}


    @{fg fill}lola@{fg text} is a little tool to send EMails.

    @{fg fill}lola@{fg text} template and tooltypes are:

    @{fg shine}CX_PRIORITY/K/N,CX_POPKEY/K,CX_POPUP/S@{fg text}

    - @{fg shine}CX_PRIORITY@{fg text}
      the priority of the commodity; default 0

    - @{fg shine}CX_POPKEY@{fg text}
      a key to popup lola GUI; default none; suggested "control alt l"

    - @{fg shine}CX_POPUP/S@{fg text}
      if supplied, the gui is shown


    You may install @{fg fill}lola@{fg text} anywhere and run it from WBStartup
    or add the line

    @{fg shine}run >NIL: <NIL: lola@{fg text}

    to your user-startup.

@EndNode

